# Claude Code Rules — Tuya Unified Zigbee

## MANDATORY READING ORDER

1. `AI_CONTEXT_MANDATE.md` — Architecture, 11-layer pipeline
2. `PROJECT_INDEX.md` — 412 drivers, 44594 fingerprints, button architecture
3. `docs/rules/CRITICAL_MISTAKES.md` — 70+ rules (A1-A13, B1-B10, H1-H7, J1-J10, L1-L8)
4. `.ai/rules/.windsurfrules` — IDE rules

## ARCHITECTURE

- App: com.dlnraja.tuya.zigbee (master) / com.dlnraja.tuya.zigbee.stable (stable-v5)
- SDK: Homey SDK v3 + homey-zigbeedriver ^2.2.2
- Drivers: 320 Zigbee + 51 WiFi = 371 total, 44594 fingerprints
- Chain: Homey.Device → ZigBeeDevice → TuyaZigbeeDevice → TuyaUnifiedDevice → BaseUnifiedDevice → UnifiedSensorBase

## CRITICAL RULES

### SDK3 Mandatory
- `async onNodeInit()` NOT sync onInit
- `await setCapabilityValue()` ALWAYS
- `_destroyed` guard in ALL async methods
- Settings: snake_case (zb_model_id NOT zb_modelId)
- `console.log/error` INTERDIT

### Tuya DP (J7-J10)
- `sendDP()` DOES NOT EXIST — use `sendTuyaDP(dp, dpType, value)` or wrapper
- `requestDPs()` DOES NOT EXIST — use `requestDP(dp)` singular
- DP12 can be pressure OR luminance per hardware
- DP4: Don't put in dpMappings if `_handleBatteryDP` override needed

### Fingerprints (L8)
- `fingerprints[]` format NOT supported by `homey app compose`
- ALWAYS use `manufacturerName[]` + `productId[]` arrays
- Wildcards FORBIDDEN (Rule L6)

### Battery (B2-C7)
- Linear formulas STRICTLY BANNED
- NEVER combine `measure_battery` + `alarm_battery` (Rule AO)

### Buttons (H1-H7, Rule A12)
- PhysicalButtonMixin(VirtualButtonMixin(UnifiedSwitchBase)) MANDATORY order
- `markAppCommand()` BEFORE device command
- Flow cards: `.trigger()` MUST be called (Rule A12)
- `initPhysicalButtonDetection()` called ONCE with zclNode (Rule H6)
- `requestDPs()` DOES NOT EXIST — use `requestDP(dp)` singular

### TS0044 4-Button Scene Mode
- 4 endpoints, each = 1 button
- Scene recall commands (cluster 5)
- Scene mode via attribute 0x8004 (0=dimmer, 1=scene)
- 0-indexed: 0=single, 1=double, 2=long

## VALIDATION SCRIPTS
- `node scripts/validation/check-await-without-async.js`
- `node scripts/validation/check-database-routing.js`
- `node scripts/validation/check-fingerprint-health.js`
- `npx homey app validate --level publish`

## GIT
- NEVER `npx homey app publish` locally
- ALWAYS `git pull --rebase` before push
- NEVER close issues without user confirmation

## BUTTON ANTI-PATTERNS (DO NOT USE)
- Local `_markAppCommand()` without `super.markAppCommand()`
- `getTriggerCard()` without `.trigger()`
- `initPhysicalButtonDetection()` called twice
- `onDeleted()` without `clearTimeout()` or `super.onDeleted()`
- Raw `setInterval()` without `this.homey.setInterval()`
- `requestDPs()` (plural) — DOES NOT EXIST
